fulltitle: Kennedy Assassination Records Report Press Conference
title: Kennedy Assassination Records Report Press Conference
description:
For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub

The board charged with identifying and making available all records related to the assassination of President John F. Kennedy presented its final report to President Clinton today. Following their meeting with the president, Mr. Tunheim, chairman of the Assassination Records Review Board, and other members talked with reporters about the report. They took questions from the media.
